quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  28,78,"O wi'i: "Ko mi okkiraa Й—um, ko e hoore ganndal ngal mi jogii". E o anndaa wonn'de gooЕ‹Й—ii Alla kalkiino gire, adiiЙ“e mo, Й“urЙ“e doole, Й“uri mo Й—uuЙ—ude jawle? ЖЃe lamndoytaake fii bakkaat maЙ“Й“e, kamЙ“e bomЙ“e Й“en!"
  28,79,"O yaltitiri e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, cuЙ—aari makko ndin. YiЙ—uЙ“e nguurndam aduna Й“en mbi'i: "Hara nun min keЙ“ayno sugu koo ko Qaaruuna okkaa. KaЕ‹ko on, pellet, ko o jom-geЙ“al mawnungal"."
  28,80,"OkkaaЙ“e ganndal Й“en kan mbi'i: "Ee bone mon! Ko mbarjaari Alla ndin Й“uri moЖґЖґannde on gooЕ‹Й—inЙ—o o golli ko moЖґЖґi". Kono hawrataa e Й—uum, si wonaa muГ±Г±iiЙ“e Й“en."
  28,81,"Min mutindini mo e galle makko Й—en, ka leydi. Fedde woo alanaa mo, ko paaboo mo gaanin Alla, o wonaano paabotooЙ—o hoore-mum."
  28,82,"ЖЃen yelinooЙ“e nokku makko on haЕ‹ki mum, Й“e mbaЙ—ti wiide: "Ee bone! Alla no wertana arsike on, Mo O muuyani e jiyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, O Й“iЙ—tinana [Mo O muuyani]. Si wonaa Alla moЖґЖґinoo e amen, O mutinayno men. Ee bone! Jaka O malnataa yedduЙ“e Й“en"."
  28,83,"ЖЉen galle laakara, Min mbaЙ—anii Й—e Й“en Й“e yiЙ—aa townitaare ka leydi, wonaa kadi bonnugol. Battane moЖґЖґe Й—en, ko fii gooЕ‹Й—uЙ“e Й“en."
  28,84,"Kala garduЙ—o e moЖґЖґere, hino woodani mo ko Й“uri nde moЖґЖґude; kala kadi garduЙ—o e bonannde, (yo o anndu) huuwuЙ“e bonЙ—i Й—in yoЙ“etaake, si wanaa ko Й“e huuwaynoo kon."